<http://vocab.linkeddata.es/datosabiertos/def/transporte/censovehiculos#Permit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Official permit, usually issued by the city council or the traffic authority, that allows a particular vehicle to access, drive through, or park in an area where entry is restricted or regulated"@en .
